      "id": "PopularPost236269",
      "post_content": "Essentially staples a [fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=fireball) onto a [drain life](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=drain life). (Yes, yes, no multiple targeting, but I can count on one hand the number of times I've seen anyone use that on fireball.)  \n  \nIce Age had something of and allied-colors boost theme. Off-color activations, rewards for controlling an allied-colored permanent, and in this case something to do with allied mana.",
      "posted_by": "longwinded",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost236269\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Essentially staples a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"fireball\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=fireball\">fireball</a> onto a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"drain life\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=drain life\">drain life</a>. (Yes, yes, no multiple targeting, but I can count on one hand the number of times I've seen anyone use that on fireball.)<br/><br/>Ice Age had something of and allied-colors boost theme. Off-color activations, rewards for controlling an allied-colored permanent, and in this case something to do with allied mana.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '236269'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy40319\">longwinded</span>\r\n                                (4/6/2012 8:32:46 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.